abstract: President Obama's latest fund-raising figures show a large portion of his total -- more than $55 million so far this year -- coming in via the efforts of some 350 "bundlers."
snippet: President Obama's latest fund-raising figures show a large portion of his total -- more than $55 million so far this year -- coming in via the efforts of some 350 "bundlers."
lead_paragraph: At the close of each fund-raising quarter, aides to President Obama often emphasize the amount of money he raises from his large network of grassroots supporters, the base of his Obama for America organization and a reliable source of small donations throughout the election cycle.

headline.main: Obama Bundler List Includes New Names, Famous Faces
